 name increased in popularity in England during the 19th century, when it was borne by the wife of King William IV; she was the daughter of the ruler of the German duchy of Saxe-Meiningen. The Australian city of Adelaide was named in her honour."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Adélaïde d'Aquitaine II was born about 1133, in Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France. She married Ralph de Faye. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. She died on 24 October 1153, at the age of 21."},"et":{"about 1133–24 Oct 1153":"umbes 1133–24. oktoober 1153","1133–1154":"1133–1154","1150–Male":"1150–Surnud","1154–1223":"1154–1223","1133–1153":"1133–1153","1223":"1223","1133":"1133","1154":"1154","24 Oct 1153":"24. oktoober 1153","1153":"1153","1150":"1150","about 1133":"umbes 1133","Abt. 1150":"umbes 1150","Chateau de Belin-Beliet, Gironde, Aquitaine, France":"Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1133–24 Oct 1153":"noin 1133–24. lokakuuta 1153","1133–1154":"1133–1154","1150–Male":"1150–Kuollut","1154–1223":"1154–1223","1133–1153":"1133–1153","1223":"1223","1133":"1133","1154":"1154","24 Oct 1153":"24. lokakuuta 1153","1153":"1153","1150":"1150","about 1133":"noin 1133","Abt. 1150":"noin 1150","Chateau de Belin-Beliet, Gironde, Aquitaine, France":"Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1133–24 Oct 1153":"environ 1133–24 octobre 1153","1133–1154":"1133–1154","1150–Male":"1150–Décédé","1154–1223":"1154–1223","1133–1153":"1133–1153","1223":"1223","1133":"1133","1154":"1154","24 Oct 1153":"24 octobre 1153","1153":"1153","1150":"1150","about 1133":"environ 1133","Abt. 1150":"environ 1150","Chateau de Belin-Beliet, Gironde, Aquitaine, France":"Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","lifeSummary":"Adélaïde d'Aquitaine II est née environ 1133, à Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France. Elle a épousé Ralph de Faye. Ils ont eu au moins 2 fils. Elle est décédée le 24 octobre 1153, à l’âge de 21 ans."},"de":{"about 1133–24 Oct 1153":"um 1133–24. Oktober 1153","1133–1154":"11